<https://huggingface.co/datasets/epfml/FineWeb2-HQ> dct:title "FineWeb2-HQ" ;
	dct:description "FineWeb2-HQ is a high-quality, model-filtered pretraining dataset derived as a subset of FineWeb2, spanning 20 languages." ;
