<https://huggingface.co/datasets/DataProvenanceInitiative/Commercial-Flan-Collection-Chain-Of-Thought> dct:title "CommercialFlan-Collection-Chain-Of-Thought" ;
	dct:description "A 183,848-row dataset of chain-of-thought reasoning examples licensed for commercial use. Each row pairs an input prompt with a step-by-step reasoned answer, covering tasks like natural language inference, math word problems, commonsense reasoning, and fact verification." ;
